docs.abstract: Daily fantasy sports companies DraftKings and FanDuel are close to reaching agreement on settlement with New York Atty Gen Eric T Schneiderman regarding claims that companies used false advertising in half-billion-dollar advertising campaign in 2015; deal will likely involve fines ranging from $8 to $12 million, along with acknowledgement on their part of findings of investigation into fraudulent practices.
